---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Masthead from '../components/Masthead.astro';
import PricingTable from '../components/PricingTable.astro';
import LegalFooter from '../components/LegalFooter.astro';
---
<Layout title="TAERIJAY+ HUB PORTAL">
	<Header />
	<Masthead />

	<!-- PIPELINE ROUTING HUBS GRID -->
	<section class="w-full py-16 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-6 font-spartan">
		<h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white border-l-4 border-[#00F0FF] pl-3">
			독립 채널 인프라 진입 허브 (Premium Channels Deployment)
		</h2>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
			<a href="/channels/entertainment" class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#5B0E1B] bg-[#071120]/60 hover:border-[#00F0FF] hover:bg-[#00F0FF]/5 transition-all flex flex-col gap-2">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-lg font-black text-[#00F0FF]">1. Entertainment</span><span class="text-2xl">🎬</span></div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-noto">비디오 스트림 허브 및 오피셜 미디어 기획 연계 제공함.</p>
			</a>
			<a href="/channels/protocol" class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#5B0E1B] bg-[#071120]/60 hover:border-[#FF6B00] hover:bg-[#FF6B00]/5 transition-all flex flex-col gap-2">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-lg font-black text-[#FF6B00]">2. Protocol</span><span class="text-2xl">🌐</span></div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-noto">해외 입국객 필수 공항 세관 및 대중교통 규약 가이드 표기함.</p>
			</a>
			<a href="/channels/mini" class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#5B0E1B] bg-[#071120]/60 hover:border-white hover:bg-white/5 transition-all flex flex-col gap-2">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-lg font-black text-white">3. Mini Route</span><span class="text-2xl">📍</span></div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-noto">거점 도시별 시간 낭비 없는 원데이 초압축 동선 코스 수록함.</p>
			</a>
			<a href="/channels/daiso" class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#5B0E1B] bg-[#071120]/60 hover:border-[#FF2E2E] hover:bg-[#FF2E2E]/5 transition-all flex flex-col gap-2">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-lg font-black text-[#FF2E2E]">4. Daiso Beauty</span><span class="text-2xl">💡</span></div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-noto">SNS 품절 대란 다이소 코스메틱 품목 인덱스 공유함.</p>
			</a>
			<a href="/channels/oliveyoung" class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#5B0E1B] bg-[#071120]/60 hover:border-[#6F8B2E] hover:bg-[#6F8B2E]/5 transition-all flex flex-col gap-2">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-lg font-black text-[#6F8B2E]">5. Oliveyoung</span><span class="text-2xl">🧴</span></div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-noto">MZ 스킨케어 랭킹 및 현장 Tax-Free 즉시 면세 환급 매장 안내함.</p>
			</a>
			<a href="/channels/convenience" class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[#5B0E1B] bg-[#071120]/60 hover:border-[#A14D7C] hover:bg-[#A14D7C]/5 transition-all flex flex-col gap-2">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between"><span class="text-lg font-black text-[#A14D7C]">7. Convenience</span><span class="text-2xl">🇰🇷</span></div>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-noto">국내 24시 편의점 독점 PB 상품 조합 가이드 명시함.</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<PricingTable />
	<LegalFooter />
</Layout>